cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.MM

This paper deals with deep learning algorithms for fine-grained recognition, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the use of multimodal data and cross-modal data hallucination, which are topics related to machine learning (cs.LG) and natural language processing (cs.CL). Additionally, the paper proposes a framework for few-shot learning, which is a subfield of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper uses images and texts as modalities, which falls under the category of multimedia (cs.MM).
